<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>{% block title %}{% endblock %} — Webhooky</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5; color: #0f172a; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px; }
    .footer { margin-top: 2rem; padding-top: 1rem; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; font-size: 0.82rem; color: #64748b; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  {% block body %}{% endblock %}
  <p class="footer">Message envoyé par Webhooky (webhooky.fr) — ne répondez pas directement à cet e-mail automatisé.</p>
</body>
</html>
